channel.title: My Server on the List!
channel.description:
I added my MortalScape.no-ip.info to the Hamachi list, because it was a Hamachi.
But I changed it to a regular server, and I wanted to delete it off the Hamachi list, but I forget my password.
Now I can't add my server to the regular list because it says that I already added it.
Please help or can someone delete it off the Hamachi list for me?
